1.Download git https://git-scm.com/downloads
****Add folder project to github****
2 Click on project_folder Open as Open Git Bash Here
+ Run Command
Step 1. git init
Step 2. git status
Step 3. git add -A
Step 4. git status
Step 5. git commit -m "Example Project"
Step 6. Go to github.com and Create Repository name
Step 7. back to cmd and run ' git remote add origin https://github.com/example/exampleproject.app '
Last step. git push -u origin master

