Step 3. git status
Step 4. git commit -m "second commit"
Step 5. git push

Using Github Destop
1. Download github https://github.com/apps/desktop
2. File> Add local repository> Choose_project_folder
3. on Summary required enter "commit change" and click commit to master
4. Public
